A chocolate dream shake with cream and flakes comes in at 555 calories, while a honeycomb and chocolate-topped caramel crunch has 508.

A coffee Kreme shake with espresso, cream and chai powder weighs in at 446 calories, but the simple strawberry milkshake outdoes them all at a worrying 800 calories.

Emma Conroy, of Edinburgh Nutrition, said: ‘Nobody would regard Krispy Kreme as anything other than an indulgent treat. 

'There will people who consume it too frequently. 

